<a name="1"></a>
<h4>Installing Chromium browser on AryaLinux</h4>
<p>
Chromium browser is one of the few applications that gets installed in AryaLinux via binaries.
Chromium as such takes a very long time to build and installing Chromium using binaries saves
the time. Anyways the package that needs to be installed to install Chromium is chromium-bin.
Run the following command to install Chromium:
</p>
<pre>
alps updatescripts
alps install chromium-bin
</pre>
